[1m[38;5;220mStart values[0m[38;5;244m — [0mseed 17, steps 4, market objects 40

  This program simulates a currency-like value protocol rather than ordinary money alone. Market objects receive
  goodness, popularity, hierarchy, risk and claim signals. Each simulation part first explains what and why it
  simulates, then explains only the abbreviations and units used in that part.

