[1m[38;5;220mWhat is simulated[0m[38;5;246m — [0mAll market areas are compared: product, labor, stock, currency and insurance. The matrix shows where impact, risk and moral weight pull apart.
[1m[38;5;118mWhy this is simulated[0m[38;5;246m — [0mA system can fail not in one object, but in the relation between whole markets. This part searches for distorted segments.

[1m[38;5;207mAbbreviations used only in this part[0m
