[1m[38;5;220mWhat is simulated[0m[38;5;246m — [0mThe final view does not claim perfect justice. It summarizes whether the simulated system makes harmful popularity, useful neglect and hierarchy movement visible.
[1m[38;5;118mWhy this is simulated[0m[38;5;246m — [0mThe construction is powerful and dangerous. It must be judged by its ability to reveal value without becoming a domination machine.

